data.description: $5,000.00 buyer incentive!!! This adorable home is nestled in the well-recognized neighborhood, Buckhead and sits quietly off the street. As you pull in, you will first be greeted with a sizable driveway, perfect for fitting everyone in on game days or BBQs. Upon entering the door, you will notice the large living room, cascaded with tons of natural lighting. Don't miss the charming fireplace, the ideal spot to enjoy those cool fall nights. The kitchen will not disappoint! Plenty of countertop space for meal prepping and enough cabinets for all kitchen gadgets. Making your way through the kitchen to the formal dining room, the perfect place to make memories over meals.  Upstairs is home to two sizable bedrooms and a full bath. Along with a huge master bedroom and updated bath. The home is a short drive to the military base Camp Lejeune, beautiful beaches, and the Historic downtown Swansboro. Don't miss the opportunity to call this charming home yours!
